{"_id":"d388b88dff69f0a8","name":"Cyber Forearm/Leg","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.65,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":70000,"availability":"","street_index":1,"mods":{},"description":"The presence of a cyberlimb adds to the Power of any unarmed combat attack using that limb. See General Rules for Cyberlimbs, p. 49 of Cyberware Rules."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"b574bce6fd41ccbf","name":"Cyberarm Gyromount","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":1.5,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":260000,"availability":"","street_index":2,"mods":{},"description":"This piece of cyberware works like a standard gyromount and provides 3 points of recoil reduction. It can be used with any weapon up to and including a light machine gun."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"62730382150f20c1","name":"Cyberarm/Leg","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":1,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":100000,"availability":"","street_index":1,"mods":{},"description":"The presence of a cyberlimb adds to the Power of any unarmed combat attack using that limb. See General Rules for Cyberlimbs, p. 49 of Cyberware Rules. Also, cyberlimbs reduce Essence loss from some types of cyberware. If the cyberware in question exists entirely in the limb and has minimal neurological connections, the limb offsets Essence loss somewhat."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"0f0d24e28dae089b","name":"Cyberarm Taser","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":2000,"availability":"","street_index":1.5,"mods":{},"description":"The shock hand does 8S Damage and holds 12 charges. It must be recharged after 12 uses The cyberarm taser does 10S Damage, but can fire only two shots before recharging. It has the same ranges as the standard taser (p. 103, SRII)."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"2cb351b7dddc16a8","name":"Cybercomm Link","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.4,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":62000,"availability":"","street_index":3,"mods":{},"description":"The cybercomm link consists of a transducer and a radio transmitter. The transducer translates thoughts Into words, so that the user need not speak aloud; the transmitter sends and receives these unspoken Impulses. No external evidence of this system's use is visible or audible. Quadruples the number of spoken words allowed in a Free Action (p. 81, SRII)."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
