{"_id":"5bbf9d81fecfebeb","name":"Eye Flare comp.","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.1,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":2000,"availability":"","street_index":1.25,"mods":{},"description":""},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"ac619d6161354fbd","name":"Eye Gun","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.4,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":6400,"availability":"","street_index":3,"mods":{},"description":"Treat as a hold-out pistol with one-half range (round down), a -1 Damage modifier, and a +1 recoil modifier. One shot per reload. Reloading takes 10 Combat Turns, but a successful Biotech Test reduces the reload time by half the character's Quickness. Rounds cost five times the normal price. Firing requires a Special Skill or Quickness Test. Cannot be linked to any kind of aim enhancer. After firing, a character must apply a +2 modifier for all visual tests for a period of (6 - Unaugmented Body) Combat Turns, for a minimum of 2 Combat Turns."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"b6f485002cd084cf","name":"Eye Image Enhance.","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.15,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":3000,"availability":"","street_index":1.5,"mods":{},"description":""},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"c0f9033b4d679143","name":"Eye L BrightLight","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.4,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":1200,"availability":"","street_index":3,"mods":{},"description":"You can also get a nasty, nasty high-intensity BrightLight flash system. Brights come in two intensities; the first is reusable and works just like a flash-pak. The second is a one-shot deal until the flash units are replaced; this puppy creates a flash bright enough to overload the optic nerves of the poor bastard in front of you, blinding and stunning him at the same time."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"663fedffbb48d784","name":"Eye L one shot FP","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":500,"availability":"","street_index":3,"mods":{},"description":"You can also get a nasty, nasty high-intensity BrightLight flash system. Brights come in two intensities; the first is reusable and works just like a flash-pak. The second is a one-shot deal until the flash units are replaced; this puppy creates a flash bright enough to overload the optic nerves of the poor bastard in front of you, blinding and stunning him at the same time."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"92358a29c96fa96d","name":"Eye L /w Flash-pak","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":1000,"availability":"","street_index":3,"mods":{},"description":"You can also get a nasty, nasty high-intensity BrightLight flash system. Brights come in two intensities; the first is reusable and works just like a flash-pak. The second is a one-shot deal until the flash units are replaced; this puppy creates a flash bright enough to overload the optic nerves of the poor bastard in front of you, blinding and stunning him at the same time."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"b24595fb9dcfcc69","name":"Eye Laser-Comm","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.3,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":4250,"availability":"","street_index":1.5,"mods":{},"description":""},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
{"_id":"842ba628483afd3e","name":"Eye Light Systems","type":"cyberware","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-visor-technological.webp","system":{"grade":"standard","essence_cost":0.2,"installed":false,"category":"bodyware","cost":1200,"availability":"","street_index":1.5,"mods":{},"description":"Eye lights, another nifty new piece of work, can be either a tool or a weapon. The plain-vanilla light system mounts high-powered, low-heat lights in the cybereye that channel a tight, polarized beam outward down a path parallel to the optical center of the eye. An amount of light sufficient to see with standard low-light eyes falls wherever the user is looking. The tight beam and polarization minimize scatter from the eye, so the light can't be seen unless someone's staring right at you."},"folder":null,"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"shadowrun2e"}}
